-- Lagarde Says Stress Test Publication to Be Coordinated in European Union
-- Helene Fouquet
-- 2010-07-12T22:13:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-12/lagarde-says-stress-test-publication-to-be-coordinated-across-eu.html

          
          
             French Finance Minister Christine
Lagarde said the publication of the results of stress tests of
banks will be co-ordinated across the European Union.  
 Ministers will have a conference call on the publication on
July 22, she said to reporters in Brussels today after a meeting
of euro-area finance ministers. The results are due to be
published on July 23.  
